==English==
===Etymology===
From [[Proteus]], the Greek warden of sea beasts, renowned for his ability to change shape.

===Pronunciation===
*prō-tē'ən, /prəʊˈtiːən/, /<tt>pr@U"ti:@n</tt>/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-tiːən|Rhymes: -tiːən]]
*prō'ti-ən, /ˈprəʊtiən/, /<tt>"pr@Uti@n</tt>/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-əʊtiən|Rhymes: -əʊtiən]]

===Adjective===
'''protean'''

#Of or pertaining to [[Proteus]]; characteristic of [[Proteus]].
#Exceedingly variable; readily assuming different shapes or forms.
#:''An [[amoeba]] is a '''protean''' [[animalcule]].''

